skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: oviedo facts
des:
Ask Alexa for a fact about Oviedo, Florida. Oviedo is a city located in Central Florida. Ask Alexa to learn more!

To ask Alexa for a fact, say "Alexa, ask Oviedo Facts for a fact." Or, you can just say "Alexa, open Oviedo Facts."

Enjoy!
